{"tid":1161273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被姊妹整蠱迫婚 姚子羚稱男友未求婚","createTime":"2019-05-19T05:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T08:50:39.000Z","uid":167658,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cde4ab8c6e9435c3d26c9ed72b63a161696a041b","tid":1161273,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"在昨晚播出的節目<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《胡說八道真情假期》</span></span>中，姚子羚答應了由胡杏兒假扮的男友「鄭子邦」求婚。今日劇中拍檔林嘉華演繹跪地求婚，姚子羚笑說節目中的求婚不算數，男友亦未曾求婚，二人亦未有結婚打算。她說：「班死嘢趁我唔知整蠱我，阿邦的面具也是即席print出來的。（男友叫姊妹探你口風？）不會吧！如果他是幕後主腦就不會揀張咁醜的照片啦！」"},{"pid":"88d00ed7dc7e539a9ee01c4f8cb9eabd47185a2e","tid":1161273,"uid":167658,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係因為呢單嘢搞表哥同男友分手，依家淪落到做私家雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多得佢班好姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0fb2c03caed7d4b89afe49f1b54c42d6a842143c","tid":1161273,"uid":116105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"成班師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f074f24b107c7aa972f3c076b170a2638f48a6","tid":1161273,"uid":167658,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"依家班姊妹肯定好心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aff9e6e1ffddf54d8e08e5144253fe8aa9dac1","tid":1161273,"uid":27038,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"43f074f24b107c7aa972f3c076b170a2638f48a6","tid":1161273,"uid":167658,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:56:26.0